<h2 style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #333333; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;'>
  Password Reset Request
</h2>

<p style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  Hi
  {{firstName}},
</p>

<p style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  We received a request to reset the password for your account. Use the verification code below to
  proceed with resetting your password:
</p>

<table border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0' width='100%'>
  <tr>
    <td align='center' style='padding: 30px 0;'>
      <div
        style='background-color: #f3f4f6; border: 2px dashed #9ca3af; border-radius: 8px; padding: 25px; display: inline-block;'
      >
        <p
          style='margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;'
        >
          Your Reset Code
        </p>
        <p
          style='margin: 0; color: #111827; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 8px;'
        >
          {{otpCode}}
        </p>
      </div>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  Enter this code on the password reset page to create a new password for your account.
</p>

<div
  style='background-color: #dbeafe; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;'
>
  <p style='margin: 0; color: #1e40af; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
    üìß Email Verification Included
  </p>
  <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #1e3a8a; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
    Your email address has not been verified yet. By completing this password reset, your email
    address will be automatically verified, giving you full access to all features of your account.
  </p>
</div>

<div
  style='background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;'
>
  <p style='margin: 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
    Important Security Information
  </p>
  <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #78350f; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
    ‚Ä¢ This code will expire in
    <strong>{{#if expiryMinutes}}{{expiryMinutes}}{{else}}15{{/if}} minutes</strong><br />
    ‚Ä¢ Each code can only be used once<br />
    ‚Ä¢ You can only attempt to use a code 5 times before it's locked
  </p>
</div>

{{#if ipAddress}}
  <div style='background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0;'>
    <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
      Request Details:
    </p>
    <ul style='margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #666666; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
      <li>Email: {{email}}</li>
      {{#if ipAddress}}<li>IP Address: {{ipAddress}}</li>{{/if}}
      {{#if requestTime}}<li>Time: {{requestTime}}</li>{{/if}}
    </ul>
  </div>
{{/if}}

<div
  style='background-color: #fee2e2; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;'
>
  <p style='margin: 0; color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;'>
    ‚ö†Ô∏è Didn't request this?
  </p>
  <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;'>
    If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain
    unchanged. However, if you're receiving multiple unwanted password reset emails, someone may be
    trying to access your account. We recommend you change your password immediately.
  </p>
</div>

<p style='margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  For your security, password reset codes are single-use and expire quickly. If you need a new code,
  you can request another one from the login page.
</p>

<p style='margin: 20px 0 0 0; color: #666666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;'>
  Best regards,<br />
  {{#if companyName}}The {{companyName}} Team{{else}}The Cotizate Team{{/if}}
</p>